    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total dream! This car is in truly stunning condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been pampered in a garage and meticulously cared for, so you won\u2019t find any surprises here. It drives incredibly smooth and has been my favorite ride to date. I\u2019m only parting with it because I need more space for the family, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely fall in love with it! Come see this gem for yourself!",
