    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanically flawless, the dual-VANOS system has been recently calibrated, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to exceed factory specifications. The chassis remains rigid and laser-straight, riding on an untouched M-tuned suspension with zero bushing deflection. Every gear syncro is buttery smooth, and the variable M-differential lock provides optimal traction. The exterior retains its factory depth and luster, while the Nappa leather interior shows no signs of bolster wear or UV damage. A turn-key masterpiece for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
