    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free from any swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings; the body lines are laser-straight, and all panel gaps are factory-perfect. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule, featuring supple, unscuffed leather seats that still carry that distinct new-car aroma, with zero wear on the side bolsters or touchpoints. Every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, having been stored in a climate-controlled garage and serviced exclusively by certified technicians. The undercarriage is remarkably clean, showing no signs of corrosion or fluid leaks. This sale includes a complete set of original keys, the factory window sticker, and a comprehensive binder of every service record from day one. This is a rare opportunity to own a meticulously preserved example that satisfies even the most discerning enthusiast.",
